European Central Bank Said to Be Buying Italian, Spanish Bonds

-- B y   K e i t h   J e n k i n s
-- 
2011-09-16T12:44:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/european-central-bank-said-to-be-buying-italian-spanish-bonds.html
 The  European Central Bank  bought
Italian and Spanish government bonds today, according to two
people with knowledge of the transactions, who asked not to be
identified because the deals are confidential.  A spokesman for the central bank declined to comment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Keith Jenkins in London at 
